quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  84,1,"When the sky is rent asunder"
  84,2,"and hearkens to the command of its Lord, doing what it should;"{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,3,"and when the earth is stretched out"{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,4,"and casts out what is within it and is emptied,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,5,"and hearkens to the command of its Lord, doing what it should."{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,6,"O man, you are striving unto your Lord and you will meet Him."{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,7,"Whoever is given the Record in his right hand"
  84,8,"shall be called to an easy accounting,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,9,"and shall return to his people joyfully."{1},footnotes:1:1
  84,10,"But he who is given the Record behind his back,"{1},footnotes:1:1